<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>아이디찾기 - 학습관리시스템</title>
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{springMacroRequestContext.request.contextPath}}/css/common.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{springMacroRequestContext.request.contextPath}}/css/stylejm.css">
</head>
<body class="login-wrapper">
	<header class="login-header">
		<div class="logo">LMS</div>
		<div>
			<h1>한국대학교 학습관리시스템</h1>
			<p>Hankuk University Learning Management System</p>
		</div>
	</header>

	<main class="login-content">
		<div class="login-container">
			<div class="login-title">
				<h2>아이디 찾기</h2>
				<p>가입 시 입력한 정보로 아이디를 찾을 수 있습니다</p>
			</div>

			<div class="login-body">
				<form id="findIdForm">
					<div class="user-type-tabs">
						<button type="button" class="tab-btn active" data-type="student">학생</button>
						<button type="button" class="tab-btn" data-type="emp">교직원</button>
					</div>
					<input type="hidden" name="type" value="student">

					<div id="studentFields" class="find-fields">
						<div class="form-group">
							<label>이름</label>
							<input type="text" name="studentName" class="form-input" placeholder="이름을 입력하세요" required>
						</div>
						<div class="form-group">
							<label>이메일</label>
							<input type="email" name="studentEmail" class="form-input" placeholder="이메일을 입력하세요" required>
						</div>
						<div class="form-group">
							<label>생년월일</label>
							<input type="date" name="studentBirth" class="form-input" required>
						</div>
						<div class="form-group">
							<label>전화번호</label>
							<input type="tel" name="studentPhone" class="form-input" placeholder="010-0000-0000" required>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div id="empFields" class="find-fields" style="display: none;">
						<div class="form-group">
							<label>이름</label>
							<input type="text" name="empName" class="form-input" placeholder="이름을 입력하세요" required>
						</div>
						<div class="form-group">
							<label>생년월일</label>
							<input type="date" name="empBirth" class="form-input" required>
						</div>
						<div class="form-group">
							<label>전화번호</label>
							<input type="tel" name="empPhone" class="form-input" placeholder="010-0000-0000" required>
						</div>
					</div>
					<button type="button" id="btnFindId" class="login-btn">아이디 찾기</button>
				</form>

				<div id="resultBox" class="result-box" style="display: none;">
					<div class="result-icon success">✓</div>
					<h3 class="result-title">아이디를 찾았습니다</h3>
					<p id="foundId" class="found-id"></p>
					<div class="result-actions">
						<a href="{{springMacroRequestContext.request.contextPath}}/login" class="btn-result">로그인</a>
						<a href="{{springMacroRequestContext.request.contextPath}}/findPw" class="btn-result secondary">비밀번호 찾기</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="extra-links">
					<a href="{{springMacroRequestContext.request.contextPath}}/login">로그인</a>
					<span class="divider">|</span>
					<a href="{{springMacroRequestContext.request.contextPath}}/findPw">비밀번호 찾기</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>

	<footer class="login-footer">
		<p>© 2024 한국대학교 정보전산원. All rights reserved.</p>
	</footer>
</body>

<script>
	// 탭 전환
	$('.tab-btn').on('click', function() {
		const type = $(this).data('type');

		$('.tab-btn').removeClass('active');
		$(this).addClass('active');
		$('input[name="type"]').val(type);

		if (type === 'student') {
			$('#studentFields').show();
			$('#empFields').hide();
		} else {
			$('#empFields').show();
			$('#studentFields').hide();
		}
	});

	$('#btnFindId').on('click', function() {
		const data = $('#findIdForm').serialize();

		$.ajax({
			url : '{{springMacroRequestContext.request.contextPath}}/findId',
			method : 'POST',
			data : data,
			success : function(res) {
				if (res.success) {
					$('#foundId').text("아이디: " + res.id);
					$('#findIdForm').hide();
					$('.extra-links').hide();
					$('#resultBox').show();
				} else {
					alert("일치하는 정보가 없습니다.");
				}
			}
		});
	});
</script>
</html>